message.entry: An error occurred building a parallel.pool.Constant.
parallel.pool.Constant objects must be built on the client.
Value of Constant is available only on workers.
Errors occurred deleting the values of a parallel.pool.Constant: {0}.
A parallel.pool.Constant requires a Composite that has a value defined on every worker.
An open parallel pool is required to use parallel.pool.Constant.
The two-argument parallel.pool.Constant constructor requires two function handles.
An unexpected error occurred deleting a parallel.pool.Constant.
The value of a parallel.pool.Constant is only available on the workers.
Folders can only be created and manipulated from the client.
The folder is only available on the workers.
The 'Value' field cannot be retrieved because the parallel.pool.Constant is invalid.
Folder names must be valid MATLAB variable names.
Valid futures must be created by calls to either parallel.pool.getDataFromPerHostFolder or parallel.pool.getDataFromPerWorkerFolder.
A connected parallel pool is required.
